<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  body { width: 1280px; height: 640px; overflow: hidden; background: #1B1F5C; }
  .banner {
    width: 1280px; height: 640px;
    background: #1B1F5C;
    display: flex;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
  }
  .bg-glow {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 80% at 75% 50%, rgba(46,170,138,0.12) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 60% at 10% 80%, rgba(127,119,221,0.10) 0%, transparent 55%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 30% 40% at 90% 10%, rgba(245,165,36,0.08) 0%, transparent 50%);
  }
  .grid {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.025) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.025) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
  }
  .left {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 56px 48px 56px 72px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
  }
  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(245,165,36,0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,165,36,0.3);
    color: #F5A524;
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 100px;
    width: fit-content;
  }
  .eyebrow-dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: #F5A524; }
  .main-content { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; padding: 28px 0; }
  h1 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 66px; line-height: 1.04;
    color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  h1 em { font-style: italic; color: #F5A524; }
  .tagline-line { width: 56px; height: 3px; background: #F5A524; border-radius: 2px; margin: 18px 0; }
  .tagline {
    font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.62); line-height: 1.65; max-width: 430px;
  }
  .footer-row { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; }
  .name { font-size: 19px; font-weight: 600; color: #ffffff; }
  .title-line { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.42); letter-spacing: 0.03em; }
  .links { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(245,165,36,0.65); margin-top: 3px; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
  .right {
    width: 380px;
    position: relative;
    display: flex; align-items: flex-end; justify-content: center;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .photo-arc {
    position: absolute; bottom: 0; right: 0;
    width: 400px; height: 640px;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, transparent 0%, rgba(46,170,138,0.07) 50%, rgba(245,165,36,0.05) 100%);
    border-left: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  }
  .photo-container {
    position: absolute; bottom: 0; right: 24px;
    width: 310px; height: 540px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 180px 180px 0 0;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    box-shadow: -16px 0 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
  }
  .photo-container img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover; object-position: center top;
    filter: saturate(0.88) contrast(1.06);
  }
  .dots {
    position: absolute; top: 88px; right: 368px;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4,1fr); gap: 8px; opacity: 0.35;
  }
  .dot { width: 4px; height: 4px; border-radius: 50%; background: #F5A524; }
  .category-pills {
    position: absolute; left: 72px; bottom: 60px;
    display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; max-width: 480px;
    z-index: 5;
  }
  .pill {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
    font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 100px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="banner">
  <div class="bg-glow"></div>
  <div class="grid"></div>
  <div class="left">
    <div class="eyebrow"><div class="eyebrow-dot"></div>Thought Leadership · Content Library</div>
    <div class="main-content">
      <h1>Curiosity<br>over <em>Noise.</em></h1>
      <div class="tagline-line"></div>
      <div class="tagline">Well-researched storytelling that goes sideways when everyone else goes straight. The antithesis of the typical POV.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-row">
      <div class="name">Jodi Mac</div>
      <div class="title-line">Founder & CEO, Work Simplr &nbsp;·&nbsp; Techstars Mentor &nbsp;·&nbsp; Host, Chicks Got Game</div>
      <div class="links">worksimplr.com &nbsp;·&nbsp; lifelab.one &nbsp;·&nbsp; github.com/JodiMac1521</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="right">
    <div class="photo-arc"></div>
    <div class="dots">
      <div class="dot"></div><div class="dot"></div><div class="dot"></div><div class="dot"></div>
      <div class="dot"></div><div class="dot"></div><div class="dot"></div><div class="dot"></div>
      <div class="dot"></div><div class="dot"></div><div class="dot"></div><div class="dot"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="photo-container">
      <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Jodi Mac"/>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
